<PB N="140" REF="141">that no</HI> DECENERY</Q> (in the original, TESTIMONY) "<HI>or Jurour</HI> IS NOT ATTESTABLE" (in the original, N'EST ATTEINTABLE, is not attaintable)
<PB N="141" REF="142"><Q><HI>with le&s;&s;e than</HI> TWO JURYES, <HI>and becau&s;e the latter</HI> JURIE <HI>is not taken, but</HI> EX OFFICIO, <HI>of the Bayliffe, and not in the nature of an attaint, the fir&s;t
